<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ اللَّه:</span> <span class="c3">{بَلِ الَّذِينَ لَا يُؤمنُونَ بِالآخِرَة فِي الْعَذَاب}</span> فِي الْآخِرَة <span class="c3">{والضلال}</span> فِي <span class="c2">(الدّين)</span> <span class="c3">{الْبعيد}</span> من الْهدى<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>